<%- layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>
<section id="about" class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h2 class="display-4">About Us</h2>
          <p class="lead">At our core, we aim to solve a critical issue faced by prospective students today: the lack of access to detailed and up-to-date information about club activities and events on institutional websites. Often, students are left in the dark about the dynamic happenings within various clubs and organizations at their institute.</p>
          <p class="lead">Our platform is designed to bridge this gap by offering a streamlined solution where students can easily search and explore a comprehensive list of clubs at any institute. Each club can post updates, events, and activities directly on our platform, ensuring that information is always current and relevant.</p>
          <p class="lead">By enabling club members to post updates themselves, we ensure that the information remains accurate and timely. This not only provides prospective students with the details they need but also gives club and community members the recognition they deserve without unnecessary delays.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500" alt="About Us" class="img-fluid rounded-circle">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
